Frontend:   Next.js 14 (App Router) + React + TailwindCSS + Recharts
Backend:    Next.js API Routes + Node.js
Database:   PostgreSQL (Prisma ORM)
AI:         OpenAI GPT-4 (pluggable provider)
Auth:       JWT + bcrypt + role-based permissions
Queue:      In-process scheduler (node-cron) for reminders/automation
Comms:      Email (Nodemailer), SMS/WhatsApp (Twilio adapters)
Security:   CSRF, XSS sanitization, rate limiting, input validation, AES encryption
Deploy:     Docker + docker-compose
